OL,5, A trial of scrapping return tickets in 
OL,6, a bid to make fares simpler will be    
OL,7, extended as part of a shake-up of the  
OL,8, country's railways.                    
OL,10,FThe transport secretary will confirm on
OL,11,FTuesday that LNER, which operates      
OL,12,Ftrains along the East Coast mainline,  
OL,13,Fwill extend its trial of selling single
OL,14,Ftickets only on its routes.            
OL,16,FUnder the trial, a single is always    
OL,17,Fhalf the cost of a return.             
OL,19,FThe government said such reforms could 
OL,20,Fprovide "better value" for passengers. 
